Ghost

What is it?
-----------

  Ghost is simple chat bot chrome app. You write something, ghost reply back.
  It is quite simple, it uses inverted index and ranked document retrieval
  to find best answer. You can modify answers if you don't like them, this
  is how ghost learns new stuff. You can export your modifications.

How to use it?
--------------

  Type something and press enter or click on "Ask" button. Click on "edit" if
  you don't like answer and write something else instead.

